Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.09,0:00:54.58,JP-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,中富葉香
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.58,0:00:56.45,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,ようこそ　葉香さん
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.45,0:01:01.02,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,私は世界に7Gを広める会 会長のポイズン・ポンタロー
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.02,0:01:05.96,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,葉香さんが史上最速で世界を繋ぐ7G回線に期待することは何かな
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.86,0:01:09.57,JP-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,期待
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.57,0:01:10.00,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,イエス
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.62,0:01:13.24,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,どこにいる　どんな人とも　すぐ通じ合える　触れ合える
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.24,0:01:15.80,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,それが夢の新技術　7G回線
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.80,0:01:17.69,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,5Gでは全く追いつけなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.69,0:01:19.64,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,6Gでは完全に出遅れた
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.64,0:01:22.51,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,だが7Gでいよいよこの国の威信を取り戻す
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.51,0:01:24.98,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,一部反対する者もいた
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.98,0:01:26.14,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,ネガキャンもあった
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.73,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,しかしそんな根も葉もない　フェイクニュースに我々はくじけなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.73,0:01:33.90,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,世界最高の技術を　この7Gに全てぶち込み　落とし込み叩き込んだ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.90,0:01:37.01,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,脳に浮かんだ思考を　直接読み取り　すべてのアドバイスにアプローチ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.01,0:01:39.62,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,思う　即伝わる　考える　即動く
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.69,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,まさに神の力の使い手となるそれが
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.69,0:01:44.31,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,7G
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.32,0:01:45.62,JP-Main-up-8-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,あの　私帰りたが
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.76,0:01:47.98,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,それでは
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.98,0:01:49.90,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,皆さんと一緒に迎えよう
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.90,0:01:51.68,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,未来を開く世記の一瞬
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.45,0:01:53.07,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.93,0:01:54.58,JP-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.31,0:01:56.09,JP-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.89,0:01:57.60,JP-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.44,0:01:59.33,JP-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.96,0:02:01.39,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,オーペン・ザー
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.77,0:02:04.47,JP-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,フューチャー
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.43,0:02:08.89,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,オーペン・ザー・フューチャー
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.72,0:02:40.13,JP-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,何だこりゃあ
Comment: 1,0:02:40.40,0:02:42.40,JP-Main-Down-2,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.19,JP-Main-up-8-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.57,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,お前将来のことどう思ってるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.31,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,こんなふざけた答えでいいと思ってるのか
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.03,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,だいたいもう2年も経ってるのに
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.03,0:04:30.83,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,すまん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.60,0:04:35.05,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,こちらは　吾野駅着く放送です
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.05,0:04:40.13,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,まもなく黒豹キャラバンが　吾野塾前に到着します
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.59,0:04:47.02,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,荷物の発送とお手取り　各種買い物など　要のある方はお集まりください
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.93,0:04:50.66,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.66,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,和代さんと御糸ばあじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.66,0:04:55.22,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,そこの橋んとこで　顔合わせたもんでね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.52,0:04:59.41,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,こないだドンゴロスの取り合いで　喧嘩してたんじゃなかったっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.70,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,そんなことはもういいんだわ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.70,0:05:04.46,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,正治こそ吉根ちゃんと仲良りしたのかよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.46,0:05:06.44,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,嫌　それがなかなか
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.44,0:05:08.95,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,また料理に文句言ったんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.95,0:05:11.03,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,作ってくれたもんに文句言うんじゃないぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.03,0:05:14.98,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,そう言うけどよ　俺は熊　あいつはキョン なもんで
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.70,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,好みが合わねえんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.88,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,好み
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.19,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,小さく小さく
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.19,0:05:20.54,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,小さくねえって
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.80,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,たかが食い物の話じゃないの
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.80,0:05:23.93,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,そうだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.93,0:05:25.99,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,吾野は動物なんていいほだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.99,0:05:29.20,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,全員木になっちゃったとこもあるって噂なんだから
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.20,0:05:29.74,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,木
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.74,0:05:30.93,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,山に生えてる木
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.32,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,動物なんて動けるだけまっしい
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.32,0:05:34.62,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,そうかな
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.72,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,熊なんてとにかく腹が減るし
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.72,0:05:39.70,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,正治こそ小木なっちゃえばよかったんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.84,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,石とか　茸とか　針金虫とか
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.84,0:05:42.74,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,ひどいな
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.39,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,なれればこの格好だって悪くないぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.39,0:05:46.91,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,それはまあね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.10,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,熊になって2年になるんだから
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.66,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,さすがになれたよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.92,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,そうだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.92,0:05:55.24,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,こないだアイアイなっ淳史なんて　まだ落ち込んでるからね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.53,0:05:58.36,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,あの夜中にうろついてたのは　淳史だったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.64,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,あいつもそういう年頃か
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.25,0:06:04.95,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,こんなことになるんだったら 吾野出とけばよかったって
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.95,0:06:06.80,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,出たとこで　吾野のもんは
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.63,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,鳥になるか獣になるか
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.63,0:06:09.35,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.35,0:06:12.38,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,出てっても何か動物になるの同じなんだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.38,0:06:13.26,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,そいや
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.76,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,7G事件の前にいなくなった子がいたろ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.76,0:06:18.01,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,どこで何してんだかね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.01,0:06:20.73,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,千倉とこの子がまだ探してるみたいだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.30,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,吾野でならともかく
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.57,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,一人知らないところで
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.02,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,動物になっちまったら　どうするんだろうね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.02,0:06:27.66,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,なれるしかないと思うよ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.07,0:06:28.94,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,はぁ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.94,0:06:32.42,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,健康保険も年金も払わなくてよくなったのはいいけど
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.37,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,そもそも診療所自体がなくなったし
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.05,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,お役所ってのが全滅だからね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.96,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,稲荷山公園あたりまで出れば
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.28,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,すごく良いお医者さんがいるって話
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.10,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,聞いたことがあるけどね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.70,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,無理無理
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.70,0:06:48.67,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,そこまで行くのに　何年かかるかわかんないし
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.18,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,そもそもたどり着くまで命があるかどうか
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.34,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,あと　人間のお医者かどうかもわかんないし
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.52,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,人間のお医者かどうか
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.52,0:06:58.13,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,人間を見るお医者か
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.13,0:06:59.80,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,人間の格好したお医者か
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.32,0:07:03.87,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,あぁ　人間を見るお医者だけど　人間の格好じゃないとか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.87,0:07:07.02,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,人間は見られないけど　側は人間とか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.02,0:07:10.10,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,その稲荷山公園いる腕の良いお医者さん
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.31,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,カレー味のうんこみたいな話
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.91,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶てば下品
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.91,0:07:14.81,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,は
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.60,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,形状的な話ですけど
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.60,0:07:17.65,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,意味わかんな
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.96,0:07:19.09,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,あんたたち
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.09,0:07:22.19,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,カレーだのなんだのって　そこまでひもじくしてんのかい
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.19,0:07:25.15,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,コーロギで良ければおいとの分　あげるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.15,0:07:26.52,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,ノー・サンク・ユー
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.38,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,昨今昆虫食もありでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.91,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,やだ　可愛くない
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.91,0:07:31.42,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,栄養価はあるらしいよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.38,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,栄養なんかいらないし
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.38,0:07:36.29,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,お米ならあれ以降1年に6回とか死ぬほど取れるし
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.35,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,ゴーヤも取れるし　カロリー足りてるし
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.97,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,それより　可愛いとロマンなが大事なの
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.97,0:07:43.05,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,うわ　てえた現実逃避
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.45,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,もしくは超楽観主義　夢子ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.45,0:07:48.76,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,あたし　ちゃんと晶の言いたいことわかるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.06,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,馬鹿にしてるでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.37,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,おたあれ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.37,0:07:52.86,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,むかつく
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.90,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,ご遠慮く
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.81,0:07:58.04,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,何があっても喧嘩は絶対駄目
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.64,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,だって晶
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.88,0:08:00.54,JP-Main-up-8-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,駄目
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.49,0:08:03.05,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,怒られた
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.05,0:08:05.50,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,撫子ちゃんに怒られた
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.77,0:08:06.86,JP-Main-up-8-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶ちゃんも駄目だからね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.71,0:08:08.57,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.57,0:08:09.36,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.09,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶ちゃんいい子いい子
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.91,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲実ちゃんもいい子いい子
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.91,0:08:14.50,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,遅いな
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.50,0:08:15.81,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,なあ　撫子ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.81,0:08:18.07,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,黒豹キャラバン　遅くねえか
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.07,0:08:20.62,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,そうよ　もうずっと待ってんのよ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.73,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ピッチにメール届いたってことは
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.78,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,近くまで来てるはずなんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.78,0:08:27.58,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,まさか黒豹　全滅したんだったりして
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.58,0:08:28.86,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,そんなの困る
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.86,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,今日ムック本届くはずだったのに
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.45,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんも来てない
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.40,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,ほんとだ　珍しい
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.40,0:08:37.49,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,今日井口先生と　進路相談じゃなかったっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.48,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,進路　それでか
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.65,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,相談したとこで無駄なのにね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.92,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,そんな悲しいこと言うもんじゃないって
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.92,0:08:44.70,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,いやいや
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.77,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,悲しいとかそういうことじゃなくて
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.77,0:08:47.81,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,眼前とる事実
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.81,0:08:50.33,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,あら　善次郎さんじゃないかい
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.06,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野の風物詩だね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.30,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,昔はシュッとしたハンサムだったけど
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.72,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,2年前吾野に戻ってきた時は
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.72,0:08:59.14,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,ぼぼ　しか言わない人になっちゃって
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.56,0:09:03.85,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,善次郎さんの得意なところは　人間体を保持しているところだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.67,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,普通21歳3ヶ月超えると
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.67,0:09:09.46,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野ではみんな動物体になるんだけどね
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.46,0:09:10.74,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,おお　そういえば
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.74,0:09:11.44,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,そうだった
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.25,0:09:16.26,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,私たちもそのうち　何かになるんだろうね
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.88,0:09:17.95,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,選べないもんね
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.43,0:09:19.59,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,遅いな
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.59,0:09:20.60,JP-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,まだ言ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.63,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,だってよ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.63,0:09:24.39,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,久しぶりに肉食えるかなと思うとさ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.39,0:09:27.01,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,やっぱり肉の方が美味しいんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.01,0:09:29.22,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,お米さんやお芋さんやゴーヤさんより
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.90,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,そりゃ当然よ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.26,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,肉いいよな
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.26,0:09:34.46,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,肉食いて素敵
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.99,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,柔らかい血の滴るようなレア
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.73,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,いや　スーパーレア
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.47,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,なんなら生肉をガブッ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.27,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,ちょ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.11,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,こら
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.87,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,この食欲ばくばくまれい熊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.17,0:09:55.74,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,え　俺今
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.54,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,正治さん駄目じゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.54,0:09:59.47,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,完全熊モードになってたよ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.47,0:10:01.27,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,え　本当　まじで
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.27,0:10:03.12,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん居残りどうだった
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.34,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ん　居残り
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.74,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あ　あんなの全然大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.74,0:10:08.46,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,進路のこと聞かれたんでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.34,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,うん　何したいか聞かれたから
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.96,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,人探しって答えたら説教を食らった
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.26,0:10:15.54,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,人探しって
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.61,0:10:32.33,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,来た
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.75,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,すいません　遅れました
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.75,JP-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,たかさん　一人占めかよ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.24,JP-Main-Down-2,Taka,0,0,0,,早いもん勝ちに決まってる
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.55,JP-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,まったく肉に目がくらんでおたなげない
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.58,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,吾野は今回も豊作だね
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.58,0:10:59.31,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,ありがたい
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.31,0:11:00.74,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,猫兄　どうだった
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.74,0:11:01.86,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんかわかった
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.96,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,いや　今回は何も
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.23,0:11:05.27,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.77,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,噂とかは
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.29,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,誰か新顔が来たとか　出て行ったとか
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.61,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そういう噂ない
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.44,0:11:14.03,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,そういう話も聞かなかったな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.03,0:11:17.00,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,コミュニケーション取れる集落なんて限られてるから
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.00,0:11:20.33,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,新入れがくれば　すぐにニュースになりそうなもんだけどね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.33,0:11:21.01,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,そっちは
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.24,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野近辺はなんもなし
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.32,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,毎日見まわってるんだけどね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.32,0:11:26.35,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.23,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,お三人さん
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.07,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,頼まれてたやつ　やっと見つけたよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.07,0:11:29.94,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.94,0:11:31.24,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,ねりありブック
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.24,0:11:33.12,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,知っても古本だけどねそれ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.54,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,贅沢は言わない
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.08,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,今どち新刊なんか早々出ないんだから
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.08,0:11:39.09,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,え　よく見つかったね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.67,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,練馬の国のアリスの　えと
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.67,0:11:42.86,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,これはムックボン
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.86,0:11:44.46,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,懐かしいな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.86,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,7G事件までは
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.86,0:11:50.19,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,毎週木曜日夜12時半からテレタマで放送されてたんだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.19,0:11:52.25,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,シュールの毒があって笑えた
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.85,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,可愛くってローンチックなお話なんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.85,0:11:56.98,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,それ同じ番組なの
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.98,0:11:57.52,JP-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.52,0:11:58.77,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ねえねえ猫さん
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.67,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,やっぱバイトで私雇ってよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.19,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,は　だめだめ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.46,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,だめだめ何言われたって駄目
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.46,0:12:04.60,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,危ないって
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.37,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一応私吾野柔術二段なんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.27,0:12:12.46,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,7G事件が起きて　まず熊が倒れた
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.27,0:12:16.42,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,ペリカンも　カンガルーも　飛脚も　相次いで倒れた
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.33,0:12:20.01,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,残ったのが俺たちしかいなかったから続けてるけど
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.42,0:12:21.97,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,いつどうなるか分からないんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.03,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,何か分かったら絶対に知らせるから
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.26,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,気長に待っててよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.51,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,その本が手に入ったみたいに
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.99,0:12:32.06,JP-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,いつか何とかなることもあるかもだしさ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.56,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,かもだし
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.57,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ってそんな有耶無耶言われても
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.06,0:12:40.07,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,くそ　猫さんって怖い
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.27,0:12:40.52,JP-Main-up-8-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,行っちゃったね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.52,0:12:42.36,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,また一ヶ月後か
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.04,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,状況次第で持った後になるかもね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.04,0:12:45.45,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.44,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,撫子ちゃん何か買ったの
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.44,0:12:48.36,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,何買ったの
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.45,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,あは　これ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.13,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,銀梅花の花の苗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.21,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,銀　なに
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.21,0:12:53.11,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,見せて見せて
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.92,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんで花とか
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.09,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ちゃんと育つの
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.54,0:13:00.38,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野で育つのって　米と烏麦とゴーヤくらいしかないじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.53,0:13:01.41,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.41,0:13:04.22,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,でもどうしても欲しくなっちゃって　銀梅花
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.38,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,でも　なんで急に欲しくなっちゃったんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.76,0:13:08.90,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,なんでだと思う
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.22,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,って言われても
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.26,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,銀梅花
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.87,0:13:13.44,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,あれ　昔確かさ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.98,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,で晶は何の本買ったの
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.38,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,竜彦の「黑魔術の手帖」
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.38,0:13:18.32,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,竜彦
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.32,0:13:21.88,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,竜彦って言ったら　渋沢竜彦に決まってるでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.40,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,決まってないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.42,0:13:25.95,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,どうしたの静留ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.37,0:13:28.75,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,まだ新聞出せるとこがあるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.75,0:13:31.08,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,ダイヤゲート　さらに増幅だって
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.00,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,何それ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.80,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,これもしかして
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.80,0:13:34.62,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,なになに
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.98,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.35,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,は　なバカな
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.35,0:13:39.46,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃんだよ　これ葉香ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.46,0:13:41.09,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,は　葉香ちゃんって葉香ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.09,0:13:43.23,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,他にいないよ葉香ちゃんとか
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.23,0:13:44.45,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,うあ　どういうこと
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.45,0:13:45.48,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,これいつの写真
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.48,0:13:46.39,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,先月だって
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.39,0:13:47.23,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,マジで
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.23,0:13:48.30,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,信じらんない
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.95,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんで池袋なんかに
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.19,0:13:53.75,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小雪おばあちゃんに
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.02,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.02,0:14:01.65,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,2年前のあの日を境に　世の中は全然変わってしまった
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.23,0:14:05.56,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,駅と駅の間　街と街の間は
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.56,0:14:07.41,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あり得ないほど広がって
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.94,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,距離だけじゃなく
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.94,0:14:11.96,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,人も生き物も全然変わってしまった
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.36,0:14:15.91,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野は大人たちがみんな動物に変わってしまって
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.41,0:14:19.67,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,まだ一応　人間の常識は持ってるけど
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.08,0:14:24.51,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんだかいつか　本当に動物になってしまいそうな気もする
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.13,0:14:28.59,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,でも吾野なんて　まだマシな方だって話だ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.34,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,おばあちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.43,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小雪おばあちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.01,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,これ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.06,0:14:48.82,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最初はみんなびっくりした
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.29,0:14:51.59,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,変な動物になっちゃって　驚いたし
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.59,0:14:54.24,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怒ったし　自暴自棄にもなった
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.87,0:14:58.75,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,何人かの人は調査隊を作って　吾野を出て行った
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.37,0:15:02.09,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,半分の人は途中で諦めて戻ってきて
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.00,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,半分は戻ってこなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.68,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小雪おばあちゃん　泣いてたね
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.68,0:15:10.01,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,そりゃあ　たった一人の孫が無事だったって分かったんなら
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.09,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,嬉しいでしょうよ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.30,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.68,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,小雪おばあちゃんだってもう歳だしさ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.35,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,モルモットの寿命って　5、6年だって
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.35,0:15:17.95,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,はあ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.95,0:15:20.43,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんで晶はそういうこと言うかな
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.43,0:15:22.16,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,玲実が歳とか言ったんじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.96,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,ホンタ晶って無神経
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.96,0:15:25.93,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,せっかく教えてあげたのに
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.93,JP-Main-up-8-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,仲良し
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.55,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.76,0:15:31.93,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,止まれた
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.86,0:15:40.95,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ただいま
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.91,0:15:47.84,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,異変の原因は　7G回線の暴走のせいだろうって言われてる
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.46,0:15:51.63,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ただ　元に戻す方法は全然分からない
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.02,0:15:54.55,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ていうか戻す気はないんじゃないかって気がする
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.80,0:15:58.64,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,おかえり
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.81,0:15:59.43,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ただいま
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.23,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,夕ご飯あるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.76,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,いつものゴーヤご飯で悪いけど
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.34,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,チンして食べてね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.34,0:16:06.54,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,うん　ありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.07,0:16:12.07,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,電気は7Gのおかげっていうか　せいっていうかで　軽落ちて通っている
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.86,0:16:17.29,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,テレビやネットは使えないけど　ピッチは近い距離なら繋がるらしい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.70,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,冷蔵庫も使えるけど
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.38,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,レンジと一緒に使うとブレーカーが落ちる
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.73,0:16:26.46,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,前みたいに何でもかんでも無尽蔵に使うわけにはいかない
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.41,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そもそも電気なのかもよく分からない
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.89,0:16:34.26,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,レールを伝う電気みたいなエネルギ　が一番正しい気がする
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.47,JP-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,そうなんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.03,JP-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,静留ってそういう人なんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.85,0:16:42.67,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,はあ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.67,0:16:44.67,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんだよそういう人って
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.66,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香こそそういう人だったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.97,0:16:48.11,JP-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,そうだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.99,JP-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,私はこういうやつだから
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.08,0:16:52.58,JP-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,ごめん
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.58,0:16:54.95,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,何ごめんって
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.31,0:16:58.33,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,知らないからねもう　葉香のことなんか
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.48,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんだよそういう人って
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.92,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,それっきり　葉香とは会ってない
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.55,0:17:06.61,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,会えないでいるし
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.34,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,見つけられないでいる
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.38,0:17:12.63,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,見つからないはずだよ池袋にいるんだもん
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.16,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,てっきり吾野の近くにいると思って
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.84,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,探しちゃったよ2年もうずっと
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.13,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,わあ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.72,0:17:20.35,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ぼっちさん
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.86,0:17:25.60,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ぼっちさんはさ　なんで人間になんなかったんだろうね
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.90,0:17:28.39,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,人間の大人が動物になるんだら
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.39,0:17:30.73,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ぼっちさんは人間になってもよかったよね
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.36,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そうだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.90,0:17:36.65,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香が近くにいたら　ぼっちさんが教えてくれたはずだもんね
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.65,0:17:37.82,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,飼い主なんだから
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.74,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんで気づかなかったかな
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.19,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,こんばんは
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.19,0:17:46.30,JP-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,こんばんは
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.17,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善次郎さん　どうしたの
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.30,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,こんなところにいたら危ないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.01,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,帰ろ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.63,0:17:58.94,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,ぼ　ぼーし
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.70,0:18:00.09,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,募集
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.29,0:18:04.85,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.94,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ぼーしのひぬ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.69,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ぼっちさん　これなんかわかる
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.78,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え　知ってるの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.78,0:18:15.51,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え　ちょ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.29,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善次郎さん危ないって
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.38,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そこに何かあるの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.24,0:18:47.95,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,はいはい
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.95,0:18:49.56,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ぼぼのぼーし
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.18,0:18:52.80,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,ポンタローのクソ野郎うんこ運命
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.80,0:18:55.03,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,あれほど7Gはやめておけと言ったのに
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.86,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,あんな企画が通るわけないんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.86,0:18:57.82,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.82,0:19:02.27,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,物理法則を破壊しかねないという　アマトの研究者たちの警告には耳を塞ぎ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.27,0:19:05.28,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,利益きょじしょうたちの不確かな情報だけをうのみにする
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.28,0:19:08.38,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,なぜ最悪だけであきたらず　最最悪を呼び込むのか
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.68,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,ビッチ　くそ　誰とお目
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.68,0:19:11.30,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,私を邪魔にした逆
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.45,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,ウニャウニャ手術までウニャウニャするとは
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.45,0:19:15.75,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,全く始末に負えない悪劣非道
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.55,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,だが見てろよ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.50,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,7G絶対に阻止してみせる
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.87,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,池袋を拠点にしてはいかーん
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.87,0:19:23.43,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,待って　池袋って言った
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.16,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.89,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,池袋をこのままにしてはおけん
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.17,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,早く止めなくては
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.17,0:19:30.31,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,いざとなれば　この体よ善次郎がこの2000系に乗って
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.55,0:19:31.96,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,いや　でも　それは
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.57,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,お前　千倉静留だろ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.42,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,昔溝にハマったところを
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.32,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,どうでもいい
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.86,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,それより2000何とかに乗ってって　どうやって
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.49,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,運転できるの　善次郎さん
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.19,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,運転できるのかって
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.19,0:19:45.91,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,むろん
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.81,0:19:50.46,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.11,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんでなんで
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.37,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ちょっともう一回
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.95,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.17,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,もう一回
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.42,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ああ　もう
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.39,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんだこれ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.52,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,帽子で戻れるんじゃないの　違うの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.93,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,って　ちょっと
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.81,0:20:08.56,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.46,0:20:10.93,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,くれぐれも気をつけるんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.77,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ありがとう　お母さん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.31,0:20:14.19,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,行ってきます
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.73,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,もし生きてる貂熊がいたら
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.08,0:20:20.28,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,バカなことやってないで　とっとと帰ってこいって伝えてね
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.52,0:20:21.20,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.57,0:20:23.08,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,必ずお父さんに伝える
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.39,0:20:24.49,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,星撫子
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.18,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.17,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,久賀玲実
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.17,0:20:26.80,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.25,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,東雲晶
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.25,0:20:28.88,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.88,0:20:31.45,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,中富葉香　は休学中で
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.45,0:20:32.76,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,千倉静留
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.76,0:20:35.19,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,またしずるは休みか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.19,0:20:37.50,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,三人とも静留がどうしたか知らないか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.50,0:20:41.89,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,おとと夕方すれ違った時は　帽子の謎が解けたって
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.89,0:20:44.77,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,吾野の塾前を　ぼっちさんと走ってましたけど
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.77,0:20:45.70,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,何の謎
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.76,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,つか学校サボって何してんだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.76,0:20:48.51,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,不良
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.22,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん不良になっちゃうの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.22,0:20:52.94,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,不良行為をするような環境もないんで
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.94,0:20:55.14,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,そこは安心だと思うが
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.74,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,井口先生　お世話になりました
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.74,0:21:00.93,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,学校やります
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.93,0:21:01.90,JP-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.02,0:21:04.38,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,よしよしよし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.38,0:21:06.29,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,よしよしよしよし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.29,0:21:07.25,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.25,0:21:10.24,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,私はわけあって同乗できないが　これならなんとかなるだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.24,0:21:13.65,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,7G崩壊のこの世界をその目で確かめてくれ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.65,0:21:15.47,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,報告を心待ちにしている
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.47,0:21:18.06,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,いいか　生き残るために最も重要なの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.66,0:21:21.66,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なあ　また中途半端なところで
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.66,0:21:22.95,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ん　でもまあいいや
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.95,0:21:23.88,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,だいたい分かったし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.63,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,良くない
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.63,0:21:25.42,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,良くないでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.81,0:21:25.58,JP-Main-up-8-2,Akira,0,0,0,,良くない
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.58,0:21:26.59,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え　びっくりした
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.59,0:21:28.94,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,もびっくりしたじゃないよ　静留ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.94,0:21:30.35,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,学校やめるって何
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.25,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.25,0:21:32.41,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あとよろしく
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.34,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ちょっと行ってくる
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.34,0:21:34.23,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,え　どこへ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.52,0:21:36.30,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.32,0:21:38.54,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,え　まじで
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.54,0:21:39.64,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そんないきなり
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.14,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,いきなりじゃないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.14,0:21:42.50,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ちゃんと準備した
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.31,0:21:47.92,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,わ　動いてる
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.34,0:21:49.73,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちょっと待て　行く
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.73,0:21:50.86,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,私も行く
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.86,0:21:51.57,JP-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.57,0:21:52.24,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,って　ま
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.43,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,まじ　ちょ　噓
Comment: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:27.60,ZH-Main-Down-2,,0,0,0,,OP前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:30.57,ZH-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:44.55,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,歡迎來到7G網路啟動紀念儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:48.17,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你可是第七萬七千七百七十七位顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:49.07,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,請問您怎麼稱呼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:49.91,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.91,0:00:51.23,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:54.58,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,我叫中富葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:56.45,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,歡迎您 葉香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:01:01.02,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我是全球7G傳播委員會 會長芃伊斯·龐太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:05.96,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,葉香小姐對能夠以超級速度連接世界的7G網路有什麼期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:09.57,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,期待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:10.00,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:13.24,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,無論何地 無論何人 都能即時交流 瞬間接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:15.80,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,這就是夢想中的新技術 7G網路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:17.69,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我們沒趕上5G的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:19.64,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,而6G卻大器晚成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:22.51,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,但是 我們終於用7G奪回日本國的榮譽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.51,0:01:24.98,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,雖然還是有些人反對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:26.14,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,甚至招來黑粉誹謗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.73,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,但是面對他們新聞學學的 我們沒有退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:33.90,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,世界最先進的技術 全部都包含在7G裡面 無限量投入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:37.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,大腦所思想的 直接能夠讀取 全部主意都能處理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:39.62,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,想法馬上傳達 思考立刻行動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.69,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,好比神明力量使用者 就是所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:44.31,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,7G
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:45.62,ZH-Main-up-8-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,那個 我能回家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:47.98,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,那麼接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:49.90,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就請大家一同迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:51.68,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,通往未來的世界歷史時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:53.07,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:54.58,ZH-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:56.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:01:57.60,ZH-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:01:59.33,ZH-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:01.39,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:04.47,ZH-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:08.89,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,未來啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:40.13,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,這是什麼鬼啊
Comment: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:42.40,ZH-Main-Down-2,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.19,ZH-Main-up-8-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.57,ZH-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,你未來到底想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.31,ZH-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,這些荒謬的回答 你真覺得我會接受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.03,ZH-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,再說了 都已經過去兩年了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:30.83,ZH-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:35.05,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這裡是 吾野站到達廣播
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:40.13,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,黑豹車隊即將到達吾野學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:47.02,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果您有快遞 或是需要進行購物 請及時前往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:50.66,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.66,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,這不是和代先生和御糸婆婆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:55.22,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,我們倆剛剛在那邊的橋上碰見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:59.41,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我記得之前 你們不是為了一個麻袋吵了一架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.70,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,這種事情都過去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:04.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,難道你正治 還沒有跟吉根她和好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:06.44,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,欸 這倒也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:08.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,是不是還在抱怨她做的飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:11.03,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,她能給你做飯就不要抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:14.98,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,話是這麼說 我是灰熊 她是赤麂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.70,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我們的口味真的天差地別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.88,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,口味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.19,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,太小家子氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:20.54,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.80,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,說到底 這還不是食物的問題嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:23.93,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:25.99,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,在吾野變成動物不也挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:29.20,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,我還聽說有些地方的人 全都變成大樹了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:29.74,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,樹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:30.93,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,生長在山上的樹木
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.32,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,變成動物後移動速度也變快了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:34.62,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.72,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,變成熊之後 我總是餓的好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:39.70,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,正治你要時變成一小棵樹就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.84,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,或者石頭 蘑菇 還有鐵線蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:42.74,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.39,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,習慣之後 作為動物的生活其實也並沒有多糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:46.91,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,這點倒確實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.10,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我都當了兩年的熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.66,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,早就習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.92,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,確實哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:55.24,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,之前淳史變成指猴 還一直都很沮喪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:58.36,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,原來那天晚上閒逛 我看到的是淳史啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.64,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,他也到這個年齡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:04.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,要早知道會發生這種事 能早點離開吾野就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:06.80,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,無論走到哪裡 在吾野的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.63,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,總會變成鳥類或是哺乳動物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:09.35,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:12.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,離不離開 都還照舊變成某種動物 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:13.26,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.76,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,在7G事件發生前 失蹤的那個女孩還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:18.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,她現在在哪裡 做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:20.73,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,千倉家的女孩 好像還在尋找她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.30,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,先不說她在不在吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.57,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,一人獨自在陌生地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.02,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,突然變成動物 可怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:27.66,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,除了適應沒別的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:28.94,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:32.42,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,雖然不用再為繳納健康保險和養老金發愁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.37,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,再者說連診所都沒剩下幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.05,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,所有的官僚早就灰飛煙滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.96,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,如果你現在走到稻荷山公園
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.28,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,聽說還有一個非常好的醫生在那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.10,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,不過這是我聽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.70,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:48.67,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,誰知道你走過去 到底要花上幾年時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.18,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,再說你還有沒有命能活著到那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.34,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,還有 你都不知道他們是不是人類醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.52,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,你是說人類的醫生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:58.13,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,可能是給人類看病的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:59.80,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,也可能是「人類醫生」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:03.87,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,啊 你說它能給人看病 但卻不是人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:07.02,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,他不能給人類看病 但確仍是人類對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:10.10,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,那個在稻荷山的醫術高明的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.31,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,就好比是「咖哩味便便」那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.91,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你太噁心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:14.81,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.60,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,我只是在說「形而上」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:17.65,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,意義不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:19.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,女孩們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:22.19,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,說到咖哩 是不是肚子餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:25.15,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,一些美味的蟋蟀 我可以分給你們一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:26.52,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,不用 謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,現在吃點昆蟲也沒什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.91,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,不要 一點也不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:31.42,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,但聽說很有營養價值
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,營養什麼的才不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:36.29,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,大米的話一年收穫六次 能吃到撐死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.35,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,還有苦瓜 卡路里是足夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.97,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,總之可愛與浪漫才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:43.05,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,啊又來 逃避現實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.45,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,難道你是超·樂觀主義 做夢醬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:48.76,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,我可是 知道你想說我什麼哦 小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.06,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,你當我笨蛋 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.37,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:52.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,好火大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.90,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,您客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:58.04,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼吵架絕對禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.64,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是小晶她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:00.54,ZH-Main-up-8-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:03.05,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,被罵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:05.50,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,被撫子姐罵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:06.86,ZH-Main-up-8-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶你也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:08.57,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:09.36,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶真是個乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.91,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實也是好孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:14.50,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:15.81,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,那個 撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:18.07,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,黑豹車隊來得太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:20.62,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,是啊 我們等了好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.73,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我的小靈通收到了郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.78,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,說明他們應該就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:27.58,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,難道黑豹車隊全軍覆滅了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:28.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,這下可糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,我的雜誌今天應該到了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.45,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留她也不在這
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.40,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,確實挺少見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:37.49,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,今天井口老師 不是要對她進行前途諮詢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.48,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,前途 原來是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.65,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,但現在討論這個沒什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.92,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,這些難過的話就別提了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:44.70,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,沒什麼沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.77,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,這不是什麼值得悲傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:47.81,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,而是眼前的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:50.33,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,啊 是善治郎先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.06,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野的標誌性景觀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.30,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,他以前可是很高大英俊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.72,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,兩年前他回到吾野這裡時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:59.14,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,就變成這樣只會「吧吧」的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:03.85,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,善治郎特別之處 是還能保持人類模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.67,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,只是普通地大了二十一歲零三個月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:09.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野的其他人都變成了動物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:10.74,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,噢 說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:11.44,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:16.26,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們不久之後 也會變成某種動物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:17.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且還不能選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:19.59,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:20.60,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,你又嗶嗶了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.63,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:24.39,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我真的好久沒有吃肉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:27.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,果然還是肉更加好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:29.22,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,比起米飯 甜番薯 還有苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.90,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.26,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,肉真的好好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:34.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,吃肉真的太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.99,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,柔嫩得如血滴般稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.73,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,不對 超級稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.47,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,忍不住我真想啃幾口生肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.27,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,等會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.11,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.87,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你這隻食慾貪婪的小熊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:55.74,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,欸 我剛剛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.54,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,正治先生 這樣不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:59.47,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你完全變成熊的習性了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:01.27,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,欸 真的嗎 別開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:03.12,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留你的「加課」怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.34,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 加課
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.74,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 那完全問題不大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:08.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,他問了你的前途職業選擇 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.34,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 他問我之後想要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.96,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我說我要「尋找她」就被說教了一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:15.54,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,「尋找她」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:32.33,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.75,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,抱歉 我們來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.75,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,高先生 別一人吃獨食啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.24,ZH-Main-Down-2,Taka,0,0,0,,先到先得嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.55,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,眼裡只有吃肉沒有別的 真無語
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.58,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,吾野這次又是大豐收了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:10:59.31,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:00.74,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,貓哥 怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:01.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有什麼消息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.96,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,沒有 這次又是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:05.27,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.77,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,傳言呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.29,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,比如鎮上有新面孔 或是有人離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.61,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這些傳言有沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:14.03,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,這些傳言也沒聽過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:17.00,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,能夠與外面交流的溝通點並不多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:20.33,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,如果有新的人出現 這種新聞肯定會馬上傳播
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:21.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.24,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野這沒有任何要報告的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.32,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我每天都在這裡巡邏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:26.35,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.23,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,你們三人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.07,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,你們拜託的東西 我們終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:29.94,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:31.24,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,我的練馬雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:33.12,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,你不知道這是二手書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.54,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,咱從不奢求
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.08,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,現在根本沒有新出版的書看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:39.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,欸 真的竟然找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.67,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,練馬國的愛麗絲 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:42.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,這就是雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:44.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,在7G事件之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:50.19,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,這個節目一直都在埼玉電視台 每週四晚12：30分放送
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:52.25,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,超現實的毒藥真的太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.85,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,這也是可愛又浪漫的故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:56.98,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你們說的是同一檔節目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:57.52,ZH-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:58.77,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,聽我說 貓哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.67,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,果然還是雇我給你們打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.19,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,哈 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,你說什麼都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:04.60,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,這很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.37,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再者說我可是吾野柔術二段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:12.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,自從7G事件之後 熊是首先倒下的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:16.42,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,鵜鶘 袋鼠 飛腳 也相繼停業了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:20.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,剩下僅存的我們 雖然繼續在送快遞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:21.97,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,但能堅持到什麼時候也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.03,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,如果我有什麼發現 肯定會告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.26,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,好好耐心等待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.51,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,就像找到那本書一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:32.06,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,一切終將可能柳暗花明的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.56,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.57,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不要總是想靠言語糊弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:40.07,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,可惡 貓哥好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:40.52,ZH-Main-up-8-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,他們走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:42.36,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,還要再等一個月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.04,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,或者視情況等的時間會更多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:45.45,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.44,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,撫子你買了什麼東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:48.36,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.45,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.13,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是香桃木花苗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.21,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,香 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:53.11,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.92,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是什麼花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,現在還能生長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:13:00.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這裡能種的只有大米 蕎麥 還有苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:01.41,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:04.22,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是無論如何我很想要香桃木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是 為什麼我突然會想要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:08.90,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,到底會是什麼原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.22,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,問我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.26,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,香桃木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:13.44,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,啊嘞 以前確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.98,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以小晶你買了什麼書
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,龍彥的「黑魔法手冊」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:18.32,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,龍彥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:21.88,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,說起龍彥肯定是指澀澤龍彥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.40,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,誰會那麼肯定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:25.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,怎麼了 靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:28.75,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,竟然還有新出版的報紙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:31.08,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,DaiyaGate 將會進一步擴大影響
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.00,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,這什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.80,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這個人 難不成就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:34.62,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.98,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.35,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:39.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香 真的是葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:41.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,蛤 這個葉香是那個葉香嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:43.23,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,還有誰能叫葉香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:44.45,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 這什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:45.48,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,這是什麼時候的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:46.39,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,說是上個月的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:47.23,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:48.30,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,完全無法相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她為什麼會在池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:53.75,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要告訴小雪奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.02,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:01.65,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,兩年前的那一天 世界完全改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:05.56,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,火車站之間的距離 城鎮之間的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:07.41,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,突然增加到無法跨越的長度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.94,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這還不單單是距離的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:11.96,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,人和生物都發生了徹底的改變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:15.91,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在吾野的成年人都變成了動物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:19.67,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,雖然現在 還保留有人類的常識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:24.51,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但總可能有一天 會變成真正的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:28.59,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是吾野的情況 或許算是比較好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.34,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.43,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小雪奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,快看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:48.82,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最初的時候大家都被震驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:51.59,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,自己變成了奇怪的動物 大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:54.24,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,憤怒 自暴自棄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:58.75,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一些人組成調查小組 打算離開吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:02.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一半的人中途放棄折返回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.00,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,剩下的一半人再也沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.68,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小雪奶奶 竟然哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:10.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,這可能是 她剛知道自己唯一的孫女平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,太高興了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.30,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.68,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,小雪奶奶也上了年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.35,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,豚鼠的壽命 可能還剩五六年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:17.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:20.43,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼小晶你要說這些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:22.16,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,是玲實你提到她的年齡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.96,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,你是真的神經大意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:25.93,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,難得我好心告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.93,ZH-Main-up-8-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,要好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.55,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:31.93,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:40.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:47.84,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,異變的原因 說是7G網路暴走失控所造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:51.63,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 回歸「本來」的方法完全無從知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:54.55,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,或者說 我感覺並沒有人想要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:58.64,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:15:59.43,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.23,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,我做好了晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.76,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,雖然還是一如既往的苦瓜和米飯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.34,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,要先加熱後再吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:06.54,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:12.07,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,應該說該感謝7G還是該譴責 總之電還通著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:17.29,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,雖然無法看電視或是上網 但小靈通在近距離能用來聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.70,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,冰箱雖然還在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是和微波爐同時使用會跳電
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:26.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們不能像以前一樣肆無忌憚使用電
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.41,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,甚至說這到底是不是電能 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:34.26,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,像是電能通過鐵軌傳遞能量 感覺才是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.47,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.03,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,原來靜留 你是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:42.67,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:44.67,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什麼是這樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.66,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香你也是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:48.11,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.99,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,畢竟我就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:52.58,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:54.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你說什麼抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:58.33,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我根本不知道 葉香你到底在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.48,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「這種人」到底什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.92,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那晚之後 再也沒見過葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:06.61,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也再也沒碰見過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.34,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,而且我也沒有找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:12.63,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怪不得我找不到她 原來她在池袋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.16,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我以為她就在吾野附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.84,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,還苦苦尋找她了兩年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.13,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:20.35,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:25.60,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我說波奇 為什麼你沒有變成人類呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:28.39,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,既然所有人長大後都會變成動物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:30.73,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那波奇變成了人類不也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.36,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,確實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:36.65,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果葉香就在附近 波奇應該也會告訴我的
