Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.17,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生 你怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.30,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,站在這種地方可是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:58.94,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,帽 帽子
