Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:04.85,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.94,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,帽子的條帶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.69,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇 這個是什麼知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.78,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:15.51,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.29,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎 那邊很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這裡面有什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:47.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:49.56,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吧吧的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:52.80,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,龐太郎那個臭小子真他媽走狗屎運
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:55.03,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,說了多少次要他放棄7G
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,這種計劃是不可能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:57.82,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:02.27,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,它能夠破壞物理定律 但他卻無視研究人員警告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:05.28,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,只盲目接受「牟利者」提供的不可靠資訊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:08.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,在最壞的情況下沒有放棄 反而招來了最不願發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.68,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,操你媽的婊子跟誰過不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:11.30,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,為了不讓我打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.45,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,用軟綿綿手術讓我變得軟綿綿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:15.75,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,完全無法控制 簡直兇殘到毫無人性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.55,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,所以你給我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.50,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我絕對要把7G停給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.87,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不會讓你霸占池袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:23.43,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,等會 你說池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.16,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,對的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.89,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我不能就這樣離開池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.17,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我要馬上去阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:30.31,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,迫不得已 我善治郎這局身軀將搭乘這兩千序列
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:31.96,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不對 等會 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.57,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你是 千倉靜留對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.42,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你小的時候跌到泥溝裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.32,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎樣都行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,重要的是你是如何把兩千系列開過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.49,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你會開火車嗎 善治郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.19,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你說我會不會開火車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:45.91,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,當然
