Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.11,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎麼了怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.37,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,給我再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.17,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.42,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 真的要死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.39,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,到底什麼鬼啊
