Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:10.93,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,無論如何 都要確保自身安全
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.77,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,謝謝你 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:14.19,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.73,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,如果遇見了一隻活著的狼獾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:20.28,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,記得叫他別做傻事 快點回家裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:21.20,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我明白了
